{"tid":1723282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班鬼點屌 我地都唔會分化  因為我地理念只有1個: 實現民主自由","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T07:49:20.000Z","uid":105976,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1182aaa422b307db468e4834d377cd1281d22c9","tid":1723282,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"出黎唔係為左聽好說話   係為左民主自由  <br />\n<br />\n我知 鬼屌你  同路人意見相左<br />\n會覺得好sad 被背叛<br />\n<br />\n但唔緊要  繼續用你既方法做  <br />\n心情差就快d回復    過幾日你睇返就會覺得微不足道 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6c9b4d97211d81cd780fa287527590835efddf","tid":1723282,"uid":310667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"不完美，可接受，要改善。<br />\n你地有無見過藍絲割席？<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"422a8ac144f4dc9a59406a088bca60861cb6a759","tid":1723282,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"絕無怨言"},{"pid":"947f33e513a551533eff55128e130dbdf6bfb0f5","tid":1723282,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">poly同cu手足麻煩客氣小小 捉鬼心態又重現而且係極其嚴重 有心入嚟支援嘅手足完全唔會介意俾證你地睇 俾你地搜袋 但係當我地示好嘅時候 唔該手足們俾返應有嘅尊重佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">不完美 可改善 不割 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但希望喺入面嘅手足 留意自身紀律問題 唔好因為權力 慾望變到班狗咁 做任何嘢諗下咁做會點先？ 係咪可以解決問題？ 有時諗多幾步已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一時港豬 嘉年華 並不可恥 休息後再出發 心態上希望大家唔好當係玩 冇嘢搵嘢做 實有嘢幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n多謝睇到呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申1999 講嘢唔太叻<br />\n<br />\n另外下面個post個人覺得寫得幾好<br />\n<br />\n我係其中一隊小隊隊長<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb6f4951a59a277abdb332ed5e5ab88f833e7c47","tid":1723282,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f63f432dcc58764e1bf6cf426bbdde82be7541f","tid":1723282,"uid":162470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf53ae98a18b0357fed8677762208c2f90b88d9","tid":1723282,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057c6c00d47851d6e9e71379eaab02185b588c30","tid":1723282,"uid":47223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"而家我地揸緊對家春袋 keep住揸就得 <br />\n對家而家吹分化風唔係分化我地 係做個假象等出面以為我地真係分化緊 從而閘斷出面對我地既支援 <br />\n共勉之 光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5e64047132b00da8c98f1fb43719d16e46bfef0a","tid":1723282,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"00eeba18ab69c031e6f497e2e1fc3008a7e9c427","tid":1723282,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"057c6c00d47851d6e9e71379eaab02185b588c30","tid":1723282,"uid":47223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"而家我地揸緊對家春袋 keep住揸就得 <br />\n對家而家吹分化風唔係分化我地 係做個假象等出面以為我地真係分化緊 從而閘斷出面對我地既支援 <br />\n共勉之 光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"不篤不分不割<br />\n不完美就改善"}]}